{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781763785209,"sessionID":"ses_1269aaa39ffe90UiGOknaKBwn5","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_7D402qFyV5tFmLE1o2aByvjS","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-review agent running a fan-out lineage. Read .opencode/skills/deep-loop-workflows/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with spec_folder .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/C-rest-of-server, artifact_dir override .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-c-9, session_id fanout-gpt55r2-c-9-1781761364358-6qni37, executor cli-opencode model openai/gpt-5.5-fast, loop_type review, maxIterations 1. Do not run resolveArtifactRoot command; bind artifact_dir directly; write outputs only inside artifact_dir.","specFolder":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/C-rest-of-server","tenantId":"default","userId":"default","agentId":"opencode","limit":5,"session_id":"fanout-gpt55r2-c-9-1781761364358-6qni37","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55r2-c-9-1781761364358-6qni37\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55r2-c-9-1781761364358-6qni37\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt55r2-c-9-1781761364358-6qni37\"\n    