{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781763797143,"sessionID":"ses_1269aaa39ffe90UiGOknaKBwn5","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_86LD6jbYwwP95LWAVxPwOEYO","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"Deep-review fan-out lineage execution for scope C-rest-of-server. Parameters: spec_folder .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/C-rest-of-server; artifact_dir override .opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/lineages/gpt55r2-c-9; session_id fanout-gpt55r2-c-9-1781761364358-6qni37; executor cli-opencode model openai/gpt-5.5-fast; loop_type review; maxIterations 1. Bind artifact_dir directly and write outputs only inside artifact_dir.","specFolder":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/005-verification-and-remediation/006-deep-review-017-021-remediation/review-r2/scopes/C-rest-of-server","tenantId":"default","userId":"default","agentId":"opencode","limit":5,"session_id":"","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":false},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"No matching trigger phrases found\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"count\": 0,\n    \"results\": [],\n    \"matchType\": \"trigger-phrase\",\n    \"degradedMatching\": null,\n    \"triggerSignals\": [],\n    \"cognitive\": null\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Ensure memories have trigger phrases defined\",\n    \"Try a different prompt or check memory content\",\n    \"[session] Context quality is CRITICAL. Consider running `memory_context({ mode: \\\"resume\\\" })` or `session_health` to diagnose.\",\n    \"Auto-surface hook: injected 10 constitutional and 5 triggered memories (1433ms)\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 2308,\n    \"latencyMs\": 63,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"autoSurface\": {\n      \"constitutionalCount\": 10,\n      \"triggeredCount\": 5,\n      \"surfaced_at\": \"2026-06-18T06:23:17.075Z\",\n      \"latencyMs\": 1433\n    },\n    \"autoSurfacedContext\": {\n      \"constitutional\": [\n        {\n          \"id\": 18041,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/recursion-control.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Recursion Control — Reason About the Problem, Audit Once, Don't Narrate the Self\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — should I reconsider whether I reconsidered\\\") is the smell; name it in ≤3 words and return to the problem. | Prioritize when: what it found.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 18040,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/post-implementation-deep-review.md\",\n          \"title\": \"POST-IMPLEMENTATION DEEP-REVIEW — Mandatory after substantive ship\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: asserting new invariant | | Prioritize when: asserting new invariant |\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 18039,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/fable-governor.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Fable-5 Governor — Reason Outward, Act, Commit, Qualify Minimally\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — do not audit the audit. | Prioritize when: the caveat changes what the reader should do — once, in the fewest words.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 18038,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/deep-skill-workflow-required.md\",\n          \"title\": \"DEEP SKILLS — Use the Workflow, Never Hand-Roll\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Never Hand-Roll\\\" | Prioritize when: Never Hand-Roll\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16266,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/regression-baseline-and-delta.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Baseline Before No-Regressions; Report the Delta\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — never a grep narrowed to your own files — and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {…} → now M: {…}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No r…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16265,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/main-branch-direct-push.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Main Branch — Owner's AIs Push Directly\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — Do NOT default to a feature-branch + PR flow, do NOT re-ask whether to use a PR, and do NOT flag the bypass or the unsi… | Prioritize when: only (the tree often has concurrent parallel-session work + daemon metadata churn — NEVER `git add -A` blindly; use exp…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16264,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/gate-tool-routing.md\",\n          \"title\": \"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree | Prioritize when: task context aligns with \\\"TOOL ROUTING - Search & Retrieval Decision Tree\\\"\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 16263,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/finding-is-a-hypothesis.md\",\n          \"title\": \"A Finding Is a Hypothesis Until You Open the Cited Code\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — never ground truth. | Prioritize when: only verdict discipline still holds: never soften an active blocker without new evidence.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 15815,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-spec-kit\",\n          \"filePath\": \"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/constitutional/regression-baseline-and-delta.md\",\n          \"title\": \"Baseline Before No-Regressions; Report the Delta\",\n          \"importanceTier\": \"constitutional\",\n          \"retrieval_directive\": \"Always surface when: rule applies — never a grep narrowed to your own files — and report the delta in the form `baseline N failing {…} → now M: {…}`. | Prioritize when: never re-renders, a screenshot of the wrong screen, a fixture older than your work making a green result suspect. \\\"No r…\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"id\": 15814,\n          \"specFolder\": \"system-