{"type":"text","timestamp":1781764118850,"sessionID":"ses_1269aaa39ffe90UiGOknaKBwn5","part":{"id":"prt_ed96abf54001kw0Z4RLs3iAJUT","messageID":"msg_ed96aa383001roOIL3jU7NQtqc","sessionID":"ses_1269aaa39ffe90UiGOknaKBwn5","type":"text","text":"The model-server demand listener uses a separate socket perimeter and does not enforce mode bits on pre-existing directories, unlike the main IPC bridge. That is a confirmed P1-class local IPC hardening gap; I’m doing one more pass for handler/provider correctness before writing the packet.","time":{"start":1781764112212,"end":1781764118843},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0b9f88f8add1abb6016a3390102e308191a63ddade1cb461dc","phase":"commentary"}}}}
